pb6182Q">Tặng Bùi Nam Bộ văn Viên phán quan tự lai dục hữu án vấn - 贈裴南部，聞袁判官自來欲有按問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-fBl5iJuTdSzvM0YZQn03AQ">Tây giang nguyệt kỳ 1 - 西江月其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/Th%C3%BA-tr%E1%BA%AFc-th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%B1-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-0JHDm0-eTVCNnxzgln5tlw">Thú trắc thất tự hạ - 娶側室自賀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/Tu-T%C3%A2y-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%9Di/poem-GRNH9SS7MhDNhNNF3-MOJQ">Tu Tây phương thập nhị thời - 修西方十二時</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/author-D3nlI_QzeVjknjQ7vGsW3w">Thiện Đạo đại sư</a>)<br></div>	</div>
